    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "Shining, slippery eelskin covers the plates of this *+1 resilient greater slick leather armor*. The armor gives you the ability to breathe water and grants you a +2 item bonus to Athletics checks to Swim and Stealth checks you attempt in the water.",
